---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { PenTool } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout title="thEnvites - About Our Platform & Mission">
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-background">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <section class="px-5 md:px-margin-desktop py-24 md:py-32 w-full max-w-[1440px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-12">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-10">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-6 block uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
          [ OUR MISSION ]
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-[80px] font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 md:mb-12 leading-[1.1]">
          Architectural Precision in Digital Invitations
          <span class="inline-block w-1.5 md:w-2 ml-2 bg-on-background h-[1em] align-middle cursor-block" />
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-base md:text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          We believe the threshold of an event is as important as the event itself. <strong class="font-medium text-on-surface">thEnvites</strong> is the response to a digital landscape cluttered with generic templates and noisy aesthetics. As a standalone digital design agency, our mission is to elevate your most important milestone events—from weddings to corporate galas—with digital invitations that convey authority, elegance, and extreme precision.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Image Break */}
    <section class="w-full max-w-[1440px] mx-auto h-[50vh] md:h-[716px] relative overflow-hidden">
      <img
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB6NxIK5vneFj7Y8ENBCtAYm0bx_WW4pFh5DtA5cc3fhElxi-sauk_Nq4fJOxAB6y6kA7_mwAdB0uTlIwULnUNGrQxRRuypmwdFl1l3kzG4TJGgea8whys0i6xH2UY257g5IsfgDnjVPUX9MUnin9PGyVGC7qQ-7qnh7irem43C7KboR9TqBN-aMaeM8dDQaxK43D5g0J4nrbZQ7iUe-_PEg4DeKwt4vDk7b32CHv9Pa72lgvS2XxYUCdpSSGGme6i875Y4Dy0DFBK3"
        alt="Abstract Architecture and Precision Design element representing high-quality digital invitations and premium web design."
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-background/10 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
    </section>

    {/* Philosophy Section */}
    <section class="px-5 md:px-margin-desktop py-24 md:py-32 grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:gap-gutter border-b border-border-surgical max-w-[1440px] mx-auto w-full md:grid-cols-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight md:sticky top-32 text-on-background">
          <span class="block">The</span>
          <span class="block">Surgical</span>
          <span class="block break-words hyphens-auto">Differentiator.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-16 md:space-y-24">
        <div class="border-l border-border-surgical pl-6 md:pl-12">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] md:text-xs text-on-surface-variant block mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">
            01 / REJECTION OF NOISE
          </span>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6 text-on-surface">Generic templates survive on clutter.</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-base md:text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            Most online invitation platforms offer "more" — more stickers, more fonts, more chaos. We offer less. Our surgical approach to <strong class="font-medium text-on-surface">minimalist web design</strong> removes the unnecessary, leaving only the essential. Every pixel is intentional; every margin is mathematically verified to create the best free digital invitations available online.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l border-border-surgical pl-6 md:pl-12">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] md:text-xs text-on-surface-variant block mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">
            02 / HIGH-FIDELITY TYPOGRAPHY
          </span>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6 text-on-surface">The architecture of communication.</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-base md:text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            Typography is not a decoration; it is the infrastructure of your message. We utilize a curated library of architectural typefaces that command attention through weight and hierarchy rather than flourish, ensuring your <strong class="font-medium text-on-surface">digital wedding invitations</strong> and corporate RSVPs are effortlessly legible across all modern devices.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l border-border-surgical pl-6 md:pl-12">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] md:text-xs text-on-surface-variant block mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">
            03 / QUIET LUXURY
          </span>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6 text-on-surface">Authority through restraint.</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-base md:text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            A thEnvite is a prestigious entry point. By utilizing massive whitespace and tonal layering, we create a digital experience that feels as heavy and permanent as 600gsm cotton cardstock. It is the modern alternative to physical event stationery.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Design Agency Section */}
    <section class="px-5 md:px-margin-desktop py-24 md:py-32 bg-surface-container">
      <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-gutter items-center">
        <div class="md:col-span-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-6 block uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
            [ THE PROVENANCE ]
          </span>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 md:mb-8 text-on-background">
            A Standalone Output<br class="hidden sm:block" />of Excellence.
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body text-base md:text-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-8 md:mb-12 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            thEnvites operates as a fully independent, standalone design agency specializing strictly in digital event architecture. After years of analyzing how premium events suffered from subpar digital entry points, we built the ultimate platform for high-end digital invitations, RSVP tracking, and bespoke event websites.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="text-center w-full sm:w-auto border border-on-surface text-on-surface font-mono text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-6 md:px-8 py-4 hover:bg-on-surface hover:text-surface transition-all duration-300">
              REQUEST CUSTOM DESIGN
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-6 mt-6 md:mt-0">
          <div class="aspect-square bg-surface border border-border-surgical p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center hover:border-on-surface-variant transition-colors group">
            <PenTool class="w-16 h-16 text-on-surface mb-6 font-light group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500" strokeWidth={1} />
            <p class="font-mono text-xs text-on-surface uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold">
              Built for those who notice the difference.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* CTA Section */}
    <section class="px-5 md:px-margin-desktop py-32 md:py-48 text-center max-w-[1440px] mx-auto w-full">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 md:mb-12 text-on-background">
        Create with Intent.
      </h2>
      <a
        href="/templates"
        class="inline-block w-full sm:w-auto bg-on-surface text-surface font-mono text-[11px] sm:text-xs font-bold px-6 sm:px-12 py-5 sm:py-6 uppercase tracking-widest hover:scale-105 transition-transform"
      >
        View Invitation Templates
      </a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
